    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      102.2,
      80.26,
      291.72,
      141.89
    ],
    "text": "4. (1) The Board of Investment of Sri Lanka shall, from time to time as it deems appropriate, carry out ex-post monitoring in respect of any Strategic Development Project and submit a report to the Ministry of Finance.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPS-ItalicMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      102.2,
      152.42,
      291.71,
      213.89
    ],
    "text": "(2) The Ministry of Finance shall disclose the project outcomes and fiscal impacts of the project to the public by publication of the report submitted under subsection (1) on its official website.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      102.2,
      224.42,
      291.72,
      297.89
    ],
    "text": "(3) Where any Strategic Development Project fails to comply with the approved key performance indicators, the Board of Investment of Sri Lanka shall issue a notice of non-compliance to the Strategic Development Project Entity, which shall include\u2014",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      133.2,
      304.42,
      291.71,
      317.89
    ],
    "text": "(a) the nature of the non-compliance;",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-ItalicMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      149.2,
      316.42,
      163.64,
      329.89
    ],
    "text": "and",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      133.2,
      340.42,
      291.7,
      353.89
    ],
    "text": "(b) a specified period of time for",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-ItalicMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      149.2,
      352.42,
      218.62,
      365.89
    ],
    "text": "corrective action.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      103.2,
      372.42,
      291.72,
      481.89
    ],
    "text": "(4) Where any Strategic Development Project fails to take corrective action within the period of time specified by the Board of Investment of Sri Lanka, the Board of Investment of Sri Lanka may, in consultation with the Ministry of Finance, and having regard to the nature and gravity of the non-compliance, take one or more of the following actions:-",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      133.2,
      492.42,
      291.71,
      505.89
    ],
    "text": "(a) restrict, suspend or revoke any",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-ItalicMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      149.2,
      504.42,
      291.71,
      553.89
    ],
    "text": "or all exemptions, concessions or tax holiday granted under this Act in respect of the Strategic Development Project; or",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
