    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      101.6,
      247.87,
      289.32,
      321.5
    ],
    "text": "4C. (1) The tax holiday period applicable to a Strategic Development Project shall commence on the date of commencement of commercial operations of such project, as certified by the Board of Investment of Sri Lanka.",
